{"tid":681274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有感而發：老老實實，班猁真係稱得上做波壇本民青","createTime":"2018-05-28T01:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T04:20:29.000Z","uid":37759,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0177f0bba8f16c80d20169148895d9aa6e96e056","tid":681274,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"1) 大家都有隻專倒米所謂女神<br />\n猁：乜柒公主<br />\n本民青：張耀揚<br />\n<br />\n2) 大家都係自己爆柒後，死都要拉埋人落水搵人賴<br />\n猁：乜柒都賴獌<br />\n本民青：乜柒都賴熱犬<br />\n<br />\n3) 大家都係笑柒第2點所提到嘅集團後，自己係最重要關頭撤底柒到自爆收皮<br />\n猁：笑完獌16強拜拜後自己係決賽柒到核爆<br />\n本民青：16年笑完熱犬出5個但只贏得1個後，自己兩隻就比人DQ收晒皮"},{"pid":"c2c62a725119ecf11e94a957921b84828588bb44","tid":681274,"uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"結論： 獌=熱犬"},{"pid":"5693fdd6f641df8d77c7689196c8fc3426b05062","tid":681274,"uid":14238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c62a725119ecf11e94a957921b84828588bb44","tid":681274,"uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"結論： 獌=熱犬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"軌=白鴿<br />\n鍾意玩內戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b0661758a0dbb7fd8cdd09227ee851bfa1485","tid":681274,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c62a725119ecf11e94a957921b84828588bb44","tid":681274,"uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"結論： 獌=熱犬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e340ddf5a4a6cba4326bb1c2a7ae477a74f0c8","tid":681274,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8b0661758a0dbb7fd8cdd09227ee851bfa1485","tid":681274,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c